Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.99,0:00:13.99,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Ice Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.99,0:00:17.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He has infiltrated Central.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.34,0:00:23.07,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}I'd like you to take command of his capture, Col. Roy Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.50,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.50,0:00:28.22,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thankful you were in Central at this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.22,0:00:29.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I can leave this to you without reservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.84,0:00:33.98,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and that boy is here as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:36.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Utilize him to your liking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.10,0:00:39.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President Bradley, by "boy", do you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.60,0:00:44.27,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Fullmetal Alchemist, Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:48.31,Default,Edward,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, that Colonel is a slave driver.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:52.57,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And we'd just bought a train ticket to Lior, too. Guess we're going to have to cancel that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.57,0:00:54.01,Default,Edward,0000,0000,0000,,Well, nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.71,0:00:57.36,Default,Edward,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this over with quick, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:58.82,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.75,0:02:35.25,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There he is! That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.25,0:02:36.80,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:56.28,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Freezing and boiling. The elements of water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.29,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:04.89,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's pretty horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:08.95,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifices are inherent when attempting something great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:11.12,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,It's called the exchange of equivalences.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.12,0:03:14.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This and that {\i1}aren't{\fscx30} {\r} the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.73,0:03:24.30,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Without a transmutation circle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.61,0:03:27.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You've got no time to be gawking!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.04,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.82,0:03:39.32,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.82,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,It should have boiled if there was a drop of liquid in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.50,0:03:44.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined my coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:48.37,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Auto-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:56.28,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Genius alchemy skills that don't require transmutation circles...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:59.50,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,...and an auto-mail as his right arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.15,0:04:01.01,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:05.19,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,...that Fullmetal Alchemist, Edward Elric!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.83,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... that's not you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.83,0:04:12.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:14.77,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Alphonse, his younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:16.15,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,So this runt is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:17.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling short?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.63,0:04:25.85,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,To think that someone with the title of "Fullmetal Alchemist"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:27.95,Default,Ice,0000,0000,0000,,...would be such a small child...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:30.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me short!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:35.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, I don't think he was talking about your height.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.44,0:04:38.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, I can't forgive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:43.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Edward Elric, the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.05,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,We appreciate your support.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:50.28,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm his little brother, Alphonse Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to make you wait, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.56,0:04:57.56,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, you're in such a rush...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.07,0:05:10.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Steam...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.89,0:05:15.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn him, using petty tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.39,0:05:19.41,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you underestimated your opponent, Fullmetal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:22.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:25.22,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you to listen up earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.00,0:05:28.51,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But you claimed that you would be able to-
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.48,0:05:31.05,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, I get it. My mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:35.25,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You should always listen to your seniors.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:36.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:37.79,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.28,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Isaac McDougal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:45.46,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a State Alchemist and was called Isaac of the Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.46,0:05:46.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Used to?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:47.61,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:53.54,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He performed outstandingly during\Nthe Ishbal War as a member of our army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:06:02.74,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,He gave up his title of State Alchemist after the war and became involved in a dissident movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.35,0:06:05.76,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Capturing him is a top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.45,0:06:08.66,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,But if circumstances dictate it, we may have to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:11.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.90,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Do as you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.35,0:06:16.26,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,All we really want are results.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:21.27,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.47,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,have you found any clues on how to fix your body?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:28.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like you'd give us time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.49,0:06:30.32,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:34.77,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What a rough order, capturing the Ice Alchemist, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:37.52,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Or could this be a chance for a promotion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:41.90,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Are you two perhaps... the Elric Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.54,0:06:47.50,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I'm quite honored to be able to meet the youngest State Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.50,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Maes Hughes, a Lieutenant Colonel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:53.36,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,U-Umm... I'm Alphonse Elric, the younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:56.82,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What?! {\i1}That{\fscx30} {\r} one is the Fullmetal Alchemist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:59.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not call me a shrimp...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.42,0:07:00.33,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Hughes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:01.18,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:03.34,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have anything to do here, go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.68,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,I will, after I do what I need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.88,0:07:09.61,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You guys probably haven't booked a place to stay yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.55,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,If so, stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.03,0:07:22.46,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,It's my wife, Gracia, and my daughter, Elicia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.03,0:07:26.09,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Elicia-chan~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:29.73,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, Daddy! Your beard hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.49,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.49,0:07:33.00,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Rub-rub-rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:34.09,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Nooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.53,0:07:38.18,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Say hi to our guests, the Elric Brothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:40.35,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,So tall!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:42.32,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,So short!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.71,0:07:47.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Elicia-chan, I'm Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.01,0:07:49.83,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is my {\i1}little{\r} brother, Alphonse Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:52.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Understand? {\i1}Little{\r} brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:55.33,Default,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,If you're the older one, how come you're so short?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.33,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, they're letting us stay. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.44,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start dinner. Gracia is a great cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:08:01.24,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme go! Lemme go, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.88,0:08:08.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:09.46,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.88,0:08:11.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Itadakimasu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.10,0:08:16.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's so good! Wow, it tastes great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.00,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a lot, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:18.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.39,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Alphonse, you can't eat with that armor on, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.75,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:29.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al is... in the middle of an alchemy training right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.93,0:08:33.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Al. I'll eat for the both of us like always, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me, leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.79,0:08:35.53,Default-alt,Elicia,0000,0000,0000,,Training~ Training~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.62,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs50\fnCalligraphic 810 BT\pos(640,596)\fad(600,0)\c&HFFFFFF&\2c&H000000&\shad1\b1\bord2}Central Prison
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.91,0:08:45.71,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,That's the funniest joke I've heard in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.14,0:08:50.25,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Join forces with the Ice Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.89,0:08:53.26,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Me, the Crimson Alchemist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:58.88,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Kimbley, let's defeat Bradley\Nand the corrupt military, together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.35,0:09:03.78,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,I know you've seen it at Ishbal, too. That hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.78,0:09:07.87,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You know what Bradley made us do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:11.32,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you killed those officers, is it not?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.44,0:09:15.40,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, please don't misunderstand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.40,0:09:19.76,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't thinking of anything lofty like you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:21.33,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,The reason I killed them...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.33,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,...is because I wanted to. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:27.69,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame, Kimbley.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.27,0:09:30.35,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.26,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:48.78,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,This is rare. You can't sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:49.89,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.28,0:09:56.74,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take a guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:09:59.72,Default,Gracia,0000,0000,0000,,You were thinking about those two, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:06.82,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,State Alchemists are called\Nthe "dogs of the military" by the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:10.58,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,When I think that he has to carry such a burden at such an age...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, are you awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:22.20,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Gracia-san's quiche was just like Mom's, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:24.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it tasted great.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:24.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.76,0:10:28.89,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd better add that to my\N"List of things to eat when I get my body back".
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:32.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you'd better do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.28,0:10:34.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.22,0:10:35.23,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.68,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It would be nice to get our bodies back to normal soon, wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.88,0:10:40.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.69,0:10:47.08,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:51.57,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,With just one more, Bradley will fall straight to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.59,0:10:54.88,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.36,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:03.35,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,According to reports, Isaac infiltrated Central Prison last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:07.14,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot let the situation continue any longer. Make sure you seek him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.10,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Block the roads and search everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.97,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,You are authorized to shoot him on sight for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:16.21,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from the Führer President!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.36,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,I... will be heading out, as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:23.26,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, relief soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.26,0:11:25.37,Default,Guy2,0000,0000,0000,,Five casualties so far. Report to headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:26.76,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.76,0:11:28.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It was a steam explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.61,0:11:32.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If the temperature of water is raised rapidly, it expands explosively.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:35.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A human body is 70% water, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry. We have to find that guy fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:39.30,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:42.92,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:50.65,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,To dodge my alchemy... As expected of you, Sir Isaac.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.65,0:11:52.85,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,That voice... Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.39,0:11:54.69,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.27,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,The Strong Arm Alchemist,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:04.70,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Alex Louis Armstrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.70,0:12:05.62,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:11.43,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,High-pressure water slashes through a variety of things!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.71,0:12:17.46,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite meaningless against my fist, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.92,0:12:26.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:30.02,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Water from a canteen, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:35.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Al.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.06,0:12:37.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We've got to go after him, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.98,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Elric Brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.78,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:40.78,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.24,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.45,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Roy Mustang...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:57.44,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...no, the Flame Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.44,0:13:01.30,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,It's a shame that I must fight a past comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.30,0:13:04.74,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Comrade? I do not have any friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.74,0:13:08.55,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones that were at Ishbal were the corrupted army and their dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.98,0:13:18.77,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It's just fire, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:20.23,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,It can't win against water!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.65,0:13:29.74,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.50,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:36.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:40.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what the heck you were doing in an alley like this back then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.50,0:13:41.71,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...so I came back, and bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.71,0:13:46.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No use trying to run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.51,0:13:49.15,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Run? There's no need for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.64,0:14:03.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A simultaneous alchemy reaction... like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.61,0:14:05.07,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:07.57,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:10.07,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The Philosopher's Stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:16.96,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.96,0:14:18.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's freezing all of the moisture in the atmosphere...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.42,0:14:19.79,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:23.47,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Dog of the military. State Alchemist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.47,0:14:27.42,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea what this country is trying to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know! More importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.97,0:14:33.97,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,If you {\i1}did{\fscx30} {\r} know, you'd understand why I'm doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.65,0:14:46.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Al, good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:48.85,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, his alchemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:49.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:50.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:52.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You have the philosopher's stone, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:54.87,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,If you're not going to tell me, then I'll {\i1}make{\r} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:15:00.62,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the time to be blabbering nonsense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:14.14,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,A skill that has been passed down\Nthe Armstrong household for generations...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.39,0:15:16.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We're leaving it to you, Major!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:19.06,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Artistic Alchemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.06,0:15:21.64,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Engrave it on your soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.61,0:15:27.86,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.86,0:15:29.80,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, Major?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.80,0:15:31.17,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:37.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The wall of ice...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.73,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is connecting....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.73,0:15:40.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be... that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.47,0:15:45.37,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is trying to freeze Central...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:48.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...no, Central Headquarters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.87,0:15:52.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Al and I will stop that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.16,0:15:54.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,While we're on that, please take care of the transmutation circles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:57.14,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,I need to destroy them, right? Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:05.54,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,King Bradley! Now is finally the time for me to to send you to hell with my ice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.54,0:16:06.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Now wait just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.86,0:16:18.79,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:26.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hot! Hot! Hot! Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:28.71,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.17,0:16:30.17,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.83,0:16:34.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.38,0:16:46.35,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,An... empty armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:52.06,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You... established a soul on to a piece of armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.95,0:16:54.75,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Losing an arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.75,0:16:57.89,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...and the little brother is left without a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:01.16,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now. You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.09,0:17:04.96,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...committed taboo, didn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:09.42,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,The greatest taboo an alchemist can commit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:11.92,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Human Transmutation!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:17.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!!! Alphonse!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:19.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shit! This isn't how it was supposed to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.71,0:17:25.06,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!! They took it away!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.06,0:17:29.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back... He's my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:33.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give him back... He's my only brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:45.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You... just took a step toward hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.49,0:18:07.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,There's no water for you to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:09.09,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You've forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:12.25,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,...what 70% of the human body is made of!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.74,0:18:15.73,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:23.28,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,You guys don't know the true face of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.92,0:18:35.99,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother... Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al, we're going after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.66,0:18:42.68,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Using little tricks like these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.82,0:18:46.85,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Did we do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:49.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:58.24,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate my flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:00.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.74,Default,Hawk,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your useless days to rainy days only, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:13.83,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Bradley!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.86,0:19:23.08,Default,Isaac,0000,0000,0000,,Brace yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:05.97,Default,Kimb,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.37,0:20:09.60,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,Major! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:13.48,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:37.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Führer President King Bradley...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:42.37,Default,Bradley,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good work, Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.75,0:20:50.22,Default,Bradley,0000,0000,0000,,I now have something to brag to my son about, that I was able to lend you a helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:54.95,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What, you've caught a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.95,0:20:58.18,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I heard you were great out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.38,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was destroy the transmutation circles.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:04.08,Default,Roy,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.08,0:21:07.49,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,And the Führer President is saying that it was your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.41,0:21:09.89,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,What, are you unsatisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.89,0:21:12.00,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,Accept his words thankfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.00,0:21:13.46,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,You've always said this, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.46,0:21:16.64,Default,Hughes,0000,0000,0000,,"You should always listen to your seniors."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.87,0:21:26.10,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, we never found out whether he had a philosopher's stone or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.10,0:21:29.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're going to have to wait for the investigation by the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.01,0:21:34.68,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Edward Elric, I heard you were hospitalized, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.68,0:21:35.77,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,...I came here right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:42.02,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how about I comfort you while you're bored out of your mind from being hospitalized!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:47.21,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they just bring warmth to your heart? These graceful muscles of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.21,0:21:49.35,Default,Arm,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy, now. You can touch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:53.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:21:59.66,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Isaac died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.66,0:22:02.83,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,He was a human pillar, too. That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.83,0:22:05.02,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,And? What about the philosopher's stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.16,0:22:08.78,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so he used it all up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.44,0:22:13.31,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, you're not supposed to be eating weird things.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:17.56,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's all going well in Lior.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:20.02,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,It will begin soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.93,0:22:22.99,Default,Lust,0000,0000,0000,,Very soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.58,0:24:00.98,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Resembul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.69,0:24:06.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The kind town where the boys were born and spent their childhood with their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.42,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Seeking for that smile that was lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:13.33,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,the boys commit taboo and witness the "truth".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.30,0:24:18.77,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.77,0:24:21.06,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 2, The Day It Began.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.61,0:24:25.86,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It was his heart that decided to step out into the world.
